{
  "_comment": "Maps tool keys in public/creative-code-data.json to upstream release sources for scripts/fetch-releases.mjs. Only living, open-source, repo-backed tools belong here. Proprietary/discontinued tools (Max/MSP, TouchDesigner, Director, Flash, etc.) are intentionally omitted and stay hand-curated. `github` is owner/repo; `npm` is a package name (secondary date source). `skipPrerelease` defaults true.",
